trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.FederatedAuthentication.FederationConfigurationCreated?displayProperty=fullName> event is raised when the first HTTP module in the web application references the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.FederatedAuthentication.FederationConfiguration%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.FederatedAuthentication.FederationConfigurationCreated?displayProperty=fullName>händelsen utlöses när den första HTTP-modulen i webbprogrammet refererar till den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.FederatedAuthentication.FederationConfiguration%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.FederatedAuthentication.FederationConfiguration%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.FederatedAuthentication.FederationConfigurationCreated?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The first access of the this property causes a <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration> object to be created and initialized from configuration.
trans-unit.target: Den första åtkomsten av den här egenskapen orsaker en <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration>objekt som skapas och initieras från konfigurationen.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration>

trans-unit.source: You can access the newly created <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration> object through the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfigurationCreatedEventArgs.FederationConfiguration%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property in an event handler in order to examine or modify it.
trans-unit.target: Du har åtkomst till det nya <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration>objektet via <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfigurationCreatedEventArgs.FederationConfiguration%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen i en händelsehanterare för att granska eller ändra det.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfigurationCreatedEventArgs.FederationConfiguration%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfigurationCreatedEventArgs"></xref> class with the specified federation configuration object.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfigurationCreatedEventArgs"> </xref> klass med det angivna federation configuration-objektet.

trans-unit.source: Initializes the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfigurationCreatedEventArgs.FederationConfiguration%2A> property to the federation configuration object specified by `config`.
trans-unit.target: Initierar den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfigurationCreatedEventArgs.FederationConfiguration%2A>federation konfigurationsobjekt som anges av egenskapen `config`.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfigurationCreatedEventArgs.FederationConfiguration%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration"></xref> object contains the configurable properties for the WS-Federation Authentication Module (<xref href="System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationAuthenticationModule"></xref>) and the Session Authentication Module (<xref href="System.IdentityModel.Services.SessionAuthenticationModule"></xref>) in a web application.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration"> </xref> objektet innehåller de konfigurerbara egenskaperna för autentiseringsmodul WS-Federation (<xref href="System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationAuthenticationModule"></xref>) och autentiseringsmodul Session (<xref href="System.IdentityModel.Services.SessionAuthenticationModule"></xref>) i ett webbprogram.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the federation configuration object that was initialized from the configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger det federation-konfigurationsobjekt som initierades från konfigurationsfilen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration> object contains the configurable properties for the WS-Federation Authentication Module (<xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationAuthenticationModule>) and the Session Authentication Module (<xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.SessionAuthenticationModule>) in a web application.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration>objektet innehåller de konfigurerbara egenskaperna för autentiseringsmodul WS-Federation (<xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationAuthenticationModule>) och autentiseringsmodul Session (<xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.SessionAuthenticationModule>) i ett webbprogram.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.SessionAuthenticationModule> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationAuthenticationModule> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration>

trans-unit.source: To modify the configuration settings, you can set properties on the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration> object that is referenced by this property, or you can provide an new <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration> object.
trans-unit.target: Om du vill ändra konfigurationsinställningarna, kan du ange egenskaper för den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration>objektet som refereras av den här egenskapen du kan ange en ny <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration>objektet.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.Configuration.FederationConfiguration>

trans-unit.source: The federation configuration object that was initialized from configuration.
trans-unit.target: Federation konfigurationsobjektet som initierades från konfigurationen.
